        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nHi Keong\nThanks for your comments.\nI have moved to the esr EdgeRules as per your suggestion.\nThe selflink serves a different purpose, it links the generic-vnf to the instance of the VNF on the VNFM (i.e. the object in the controller), whereas the relationship will link the generic-vnf to the VNFM (i.e. to the controller)",
